OL,4,Cdeath detained in hospital
OL,6,FA man who stabbed his 71-year-old
OL,7,Fmother to death in their family home
OL,8,Fafter having paranoid delusions has
OL,9,Fbeen handed a hospital order.
OL,11,FShaun Emmerson, 51, stabbed Christine
OL,12,FEmmerson 35 times in her neck and
OL,13,Ftorso with a kitchen knife in
OL,14,FLincolnshire on August 3 last year.
OL,16,FThe court heard he then climbed on to
OL,17,Fthe conservatory roof and called 999
OL,18,Fto admit to the "violent attack".
