OL,3,CMan who stabbed 71-year-old mother to
OL,4,Cdeath detained in hospital
OL,6,FSentencing Emmerson at Lincoln Crown
OL,7,FCourt on Tuesday, Judge Simon Hirst
OL,8,Fhanded him an indefinite order to be
OL,9,Fdetained in hospital, where he will be
OL,10,Ftreated for his paranoid schizophrenia.
OL,12,FThe jury in a fact-finding hearing had
OL,13,Fpreviously found Emmerson, of Kirk
OL,14,FClose, West Ashby, Lincolnshire, did
OL,15,Fthe act alleged against him.
OL,17,FJurors heard Emmerson thought he could
OL,18,Fhear his neighbours through the walls
OL,19,Fsay they wanted to kill him in a
OL,20,F"painful" way and believed that people
OL,21,Fwould "attack" him in his sleep.
