OL,6,FIn a 999 call played in court Emmerson
OL,7,Fcould be heard asking the police
OL,8,Foperator to send armed officers to
OL,9,F"put me out of my misery."
OL,11,FHe also claimed the "Department of
OL,12,FJustice have been torturing me for the
OL,13,Flast 20 years".
OL,15,FEmmerson, who was experiencing a
OL,16,Fpsychotic episode when he killed his
OL,17,Fmother, was ruled unfit to enter a
OL,18,Fplea to the charge of murder or take
OL,19,Fpart in the trial because of his
OL,20,Fmental illness.
