OL,6,FThe three-day trial of facts asked
OL,7,Fjurors to decide whether Emmerson "did
OL,8,Fthe acts alleged against him", rather
OL,9,Fthan find him guilty or not guilty.
OL,11,FThe defendant, who appeared by video
OL,12,Flink on Tuesday from Arnold Lodge, a
OL,13,Fmedium secure hospital in
OL,14,FLincolnshire, spoke only to confirm
OL,15,Fhis name.
OL,17,FJudge Hirst told the defendant: "On
OL,18,F11th July, the jury found you killed
OL,19,Fyour mum. You rang the police and told
OL,20,Fthem you attacked your mum with a
OL,21,Fknife.
