OL,6,F"I am satisfied that you are suffering
OL,7,Ffrom a mental disorder, namely
OL,8,Fparanoid schizophrenia. You will be
OL,9,Freadmitted to Arnold Lodge and
OL,10,Fdetained at Arnold Lodge."
OL,12,FThe judge commended the dignity of
OL,13,FEmmerson's family members present in
OL,14,Fthe court and said "the emotions must
OL,15,Fbe very mixed indeed" and that it had
OL,16,Fbeen an "incredibly difficult" case.
